-- Ma’aden Awards Contract to Bechtel for Mining City, Watan Says
-- B y   G l e n   C a r e y
-- 2012-05-02T06:01:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-02/ma-aden-awards-contract-to-bechtel-for-mining-city-watan-says.html
Saudi Arabian Mining Co. (MAADEN) , know as
Ma’aden, awarded an engineering services contract to Bechtel
Group Inc. for a planned industrial city for mining companies,
 al-Watan  said, citing a statement from the company.  The city in the north of Saudi Arabia will include an
industrial area for manufacturing and support and housing and
commercial facilities, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Glen Carey in Riyadh at 
 gcarey8@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew J. Barden at 
 barden@bloomberg.net  